oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tank in front of Bonnie Kate Theatre
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Tank in front of Bonnie Kate Theatre on Sycamore. It was there to promote the sale of bonds and collect scrap iron. Movie playing was "To Hell and Back."
